								<div class="elementor-text-editor elementor-clearfix">
				<p>We deliver parcels to thousands of homes across the world every day, and with access to DHL’s unrivalled network, we now deliver further afield as well, with 180 countries within easy reach.</p>
<p>On top of that, we collect and process 950 million mail items every year. So whether you are sending a parcel, letter or packet – we have a service that’s right for you.</p>
<p>We believe that sending and receiving parcels should be simple, and strive to deliver a convenient and flexible service which fits in with the busy lifestyles of consumers.</p>
<p>That’s why we are the delivery partner of choice for a large number of retailers, with SMEs right through to global brands relying on our delivery expertise to get their parcels out to customers.</p>
<p>And our expertise do not stop with parcels. As a trusted mail provider, our customers enjoy significant costs savings, convenient collection times, mail tracking and dedicated support teams.</p>					</div>
